3. Issues / Blockers
- SEN12MS dataset is too large — selective download method required  
- Jetson Nano needs compatible JetPack version  
- Need to finalize whether TensorRT conversion uses FP16 or INT8  


4. Decisions Made
- YOLOv8-n selected due to best performance on Jetson Nano  
- NDVI estimator will start with RGB→NDVI regression and VARI baseline  
- Jetson Nano responsibilities to be shared between **AbuBaker & Ahmed**  
- Initial results (graphs, screenshots, logs) will be pushed to /results  


5. Goals for Next Week
- Finish first YOLOv8-n training run  
- Generate sample NDVI-vs-ground-truth comparison  
- Validate Jetson Nano GPU acceleration + FPS benchmark  



