| Meeting Documentation | Record and upload MoM                       | Abeer |

---

## Expected Outcomes (Phase 3)
- YOLO training accuracy and loss curves  
- NDVI vs ground truth comparison plots  
- Jetson Nano real-time FPS and latency results  
- Organized results directory for final reporting  

